      EMV_AB
      搜寻A型卡和B型卡一次；此模式为EMV寻卡模式，通常使用该模式;

      ISO14443_AB

      Detect type A card for once, and detect type B card for once; This mode is used to tighten the function for mutiple cards detecting.
